-    * ``--session-timeout SECONDS`` (or ``--session-timeout=SECONDS``)
-    * ``--permission-mode MODE``
-    * ``--name NAME``
-    * ``--spawn {session,same-dir,worktree}``
-    * ``--capacity N``
-    * ``--create-session-in-dir`` / ``--no-create-session-in-dir``
-    * ``--help`` / ``-h``
-
